#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/units/Dismounted_Commander.cfg:113
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/units/Dismounted_Commander.cfg:235
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/units/Horseman_Commander.cfg:37
